WEBVTT

01:37.880 --> 01:41.030
[The Epoch of Miyu]

01:41.070 --> 01:43.970
[Episode 13]

01:54.720 --> 01:55.310
Mr. Ji,

01:56.560 --> 01:57.759
please wait a moment.

02:02.190 --> 02:04.540
This is the money
I borrowed from you last time.

02:04.540 --> 02:05.960
There's no need to rush to pay me back.

02:05.960 --> 02:07.130
Please take it.

02:07.150 --> 02:09.220
Otherwise, I'll feel bad.

02:12.230 --> 02:12.780
Okay.

02:15.590 --> 02:16.920
Is there anything else?

02:20.430 --> 02:22.690
Have the linens in the room been changed?

02:23.000 --> 02:23.420
Yes, they have.

02:23.420 --> 02:24.550
What did the guest say?

02:24.550 --> 02:26.210
No negative feedback for now.

02:28.560 --> 02:28.960
Okay.

02:29.630 --> 02:30.760
Go back to your work.

02:38.550 --> 02:40.410
You're getting off work soon too.

02:47.590 --> 02:49.010
Yunhai Cotton Textile Factory

02:49.010 --> 02:50.240
is a solid partner.

02:50.870 --> 02:52.010
This time, the PR crisis

02:52.010 --> 02:53.820
was handled smoothly in the end.

02:56.240 --> 02:57.190
Thanks to you.

02:57.960 --> 02:58.560
Thank you.

02:59.079 --> 02:59.740
No problem.

03:02.310 --> 03:03.030
What about the linens

03:03.030 --> 03:04.800
you ordered from abroad?

03:04.910 --> 03:05.960
They are also in storage.

03:05.960 --> 03:06.710
Shanghai is humid,

03:06.710 --> 03:08.970
so it's always right to have an extra set.

03:10.120 --> 03:12.430
How come you know so much about linens?

03:13.950 --> 03:15.550
Shouldn't I know about them?

03:16.310 --> 03:17.640
That's not what I meant.

03:20.000 --> 03:22.430
I used to work at Purong Hotel

03:22.840 --> 03:24.960
as an attendant for many years.

03:25.500 --> 03:26.500
I've experienced

03:26.870 --> 03:27.960
all the work you've done

03:27.960 --> 03:29.240
and the mistakes you've made.

03:29.240 --> 03:30.310
No wonder.

03:30.600 --> 03:31.430
No wonder what?

03:31.430 --> 03:32.460
No wonder

03:32.630 --> 03:34.960
you can always find
so many faults with me.

03:35.280 --> 03:35.960
I can't help it.

03:35.960 --> 03:37.640
It's your first time being a forewoman.

03:37.640 --> 03:39.850
And it's my first time officially
being a general manager.

03:39.850 --> 03:41.079
Let's help each other

03:41.360 --> 03:42.760
and bear with each other.

03:47.910 --> 03:50.240
Actually, what I want to do
is very simple.

03:50.430 --> 03:52.290
I just want to be a good forewoman.

03:53.630 --> 03:54.700
But...

03:55.310 --> 03:55.910
But what?

03:57.010 --> 03:58.079
But we got through

03:58.079 --> 03:59.400
this crisis together

03:59.400 --> 04:00.930
as a whole executive floor.

04:00.960 --> 04:03.080
But I was the only one who got the bonus.

04:03.080 --> 04:05.840
Everyone thinks I got it
through connections.

04:07.870 --> 04:09.280
What do you think then?

04:10.630 --> 04:11.750
If you think I gave you that bonus

04:11.750 --> 04:12.910
because I've lost my mind

04:12.910 --> 04:14.150
or was playing favorites,

04:14.150 --> 04:15.400
and you really don't want it,

04:15.400 --> 04:17.060
you can return it to the hotel.

04:17.290 --> 04:18.310
If you had the guts to play favorites,

04:18.310 --> 04:20.310
I wouldn't dare to receive it, okay?

04:22.950 --> 04:24.950
You really are quite different.

04:25.470 --> 04:26.800
Others bully the weak and fear the strong,

04:26.800 --> 04:28.600
but you do the exact opposite.

04:29.500 --> 04:30.390
If you used this momentum

04:30.390 --> 04:32.830
to manage your subordinates,
it would be great.

04:32.830 --> 04:33.490
Look at you.

04:33.510 --> 04:35.990
You act like being a forewoman
is accumulating karma.

04:35.990 --> 04:36.830
You are everywhere—

04:36.830 --> 04:37.680
working overtime,

04:37.680 --> 04:38.159
covering shifts,

04:38.159 --> 04:38.920
taking extra duty…

04:38.920 --> 04:41.390
You don't seriously think
the executive floor

04:41.390 --> 04:42.870
can keep everything running smoothly

04:42.870 --> 04:44.430
just by this kind of
unconditional self-sacrifice, do you?

04:44.430 --> 04:45.600
I know.

04:45.600 --> 04:47.510
Sometimes I want to be tough too.

04:47.590 --> 04:50.780
But if they don't respect me
from the bottom of their hearts,

04:50.780 --> 04:53.159
my toughness is just a bluff.

04:53.270 --> 04:55.610
I just want to use my own ability

04:55.630 --> 04:58.000
to prove that I deserve
to be in this position.

04:58.000 --> 04:58.860
How to prove it?

04:59.560 --> 05:00.820
By pleasing everyone?

05:02.040 --> 05:02.800
I admit,

05:02.800 --> 05:04.360
I can't suddenly become someone

05:04.360 --> 05:05.720
who ignores others' opinions

05:05.720 --> 05:06.920
and lays down the law.

05:07.240 --> 05:08.430
But that might not be the only way

05:08.430 --> 05:10.000
to be a good forewoman.

05:11.070 --> 05:13.720
I just want to find a way that suits me.

05:15.890 --> 05:17.570
Let me give you some advice.

05:18.180 --> 05:19.240
Before you've fully

05:19.240 --> 05:21.190
established your authority,

05:21.480 --> 05:22.870
rumors like people saying

05:22.870 --> 05:24.190
you got here through connections

05:24.190 --> 05:25.830
aren't entirely bad.

05:26.560 --> 05:29.040
It all depends on how you use them—

05:29.190 --> 05:32.070
handled well, they can actually
work to your advantage.

05:32.070 --> 05:33.159
What do you mean?

05:34.270 --> 05:35.120
Keep it up.

05:46.870 --> 05:49.800
According to Article 47

05:49.800 --> 05:50.700
of the Purong Hotel Quality Management
Rewards and Penalties Policy,

05:50.700 --> 05:56.490
[Purong Hotel]

05:50.830 --> 05:52.070
if management is negligent,

05:52.070 --> 05:53.270
dereliction of duty,

05:53.630 --> 05:54.690
and command errors

05:55.000 --> 05:56.130
that cause the hotel

05:56.240 --> 05:58.770
serious financial and reputational losses,

05:59.630 --> 06:01.160
they shall face
severe disciplinary action,

06:01.160 --> 06:03.240
including demotion
or removal from their position.

06:03.240 --> 06:04.120
Mr. Ji,

06:04.310 --> 06:06.070
do you want me

06:06.070 --> 06:08.270
to bear such a big responsibility alone?

06:08.270 --> 06:11.430
I'm just a junior
HSKP Department manager.

06:11.430 --> 06:14.160
I can't take on such a big responsibility.

06:14.160 --> 06:15.950
This large-scale linen replacement alone

06:15.950 --> 06:18.600
comes with a cost difference of over
a million just from the turnover.

06:18.600 --> 06:20.540
On top of that, there are
the PR crisis media expenses,

06:20.540 --> 06:22.630
the costs of the
complimentary stay promotions,

06:22.630 --> 06:24.680
and the contract fees
for switching laundry vendors.

06:24.130 --> 06:26.090
[Purong Hotel]

06:26.430 --> 06:27.360
HSKP Department

06:27.800 --> 06:30.560
is tied to a huge portion
of the hotel's revenue and cash flow.

06:30.560 --> 06:31.430
You know that.

06:32.070 --> 06:32.800
I...

06:33.920 --> 06:34.640
Mr. Ji,

06:35.159 --> 06:36.630
don't scare Mr. Feng.

06:37.000 --> 06:40.360
Anyone hearing this might think you're
about to audit him down to the last penny.

06:40.360 --> 06:42.830
Besides, if the books
aren't settled by year-end,

06:42.830 --> 06:44.730
you can't really tell
profit from loss anyway,

06:44.730 --> 06:45.530
right?

06:46.120 --> 06:47.159
We know

06:47.430 --> 06:49.430
you've just taken office,

06:49.430 --> 06:50.920
so you're sweeping clean.

06:51.720 --> 06:53.000
We all understand.

06:53.159 --> 06:54.159
But

06:54.310 --> 06:55.920
we do hope you can also

06:55.920 --> 06:58.630
appreciate how difficult things
are for those of us working under you.

06:58.630 --> 06:59.870
Some things

06:59.870 --> 07:01.830
may sound easy to say,

07:01.830 --> 07:03.680
but they're not nearly
as simple to carry out.

07:03.680 --> 07:06.680
It is inevitable to make mistakes at work.

07:06.710 --> 07:08.540
Please go easy on us, Mr. Ji.

07:08.920 --> 07:09.430
Yeah.

07:09.720 --> 07:10.950
If we strictly

07:10.950 --> 07:12.190
follow the rules,

07:12.430 --> 07:14.090
none of us will make any money.

07:14.190 --> 07:14.750
You might as well

07:14.750 --> 07:15.920
just fine us all.

07:23.240 --> 07:24.000
Fine.

07:24.390 --> 07:27.000
I respect everyone's opinion.

07:28.550 --> 07:30.810
Then keep your position as Director Feng

07:30.930 --> 07:33.260
but his quarterly bonus will be deducted.

07:33.600 --> 07:34.750
He'll be given a major demerit

07:34.750 --> 07:36.350
and a hotel-wide criticism.

07:36.920 --> 07:37.850
Any objections?

07:48.040 --> 07:49.190
I scheduled a shift for you,

07:49.190 --> 07:50.520
and you're being picky?

07:50.720 --> 07:52.360
Do I have to beg you to work?

07:52.950 --> 07:55.240
Director, I really can't
work the night shift today.

07:55.240 --> 07:56.600
If you can't work, then get out!

07:56.600 --> 07:57.740
Get as far away as possible!

07:57.740 --> 07:58.630
I'm sorry.

08:07.830 --> 08:08.830
What are you staring at?

08:08.830 --> 08:10.160
Don't you know me?

08:10.190 --> 08:11.850
If you're not eating, get out!

08:15.800 --> 08:17.360
What kind of crappy food is this?

08:17.360 --> 08:18.430
I'm not eating!

08:22.770 --> 08:24.100
What are you looking at?

08:24.370 --> 08:25.460
Just eat!

08:31.600 --> 08:33.150
Is that drunkard Feng crazy?

08:33.150 --> 08:34.440
Why is he yelling at everyone?

08:34.440 --> 08:35.440
Didn't you know?

08:35.440 --> 08:36.840
Because of the bleach incident,

08:36.840 --> 08:38.630
he was publicly criticized
by the whole hotel.

08:38.630 --> 08:40.559
The penalty is still posted
on the official website.

08:40.559 --> 08:42.750
Everyone knows he's
a parasite in the hotel.

08:42.750 --> 08:44.810
Someone finally taught him a lesson.

08:45.200 --> 08:47.800
Then I must order a milk tea
to celebrate today.

08:47.870 --> 08:48.790
Count me in.

08:59.890 --> 09:00.690
From today on,

09:01.510 --> 09:03.720
please have all departments
follow the Purong Hotel service rules

09:03.720 --> 09:04.500
to self-check for issues.

09:04.430 --> 09:07.280
[Purong Hotel]

09:04.920 --> 09:06.150
Strengthen management,

09:06.150 --> 09:07.670
upgrade basic employee training,

09:07.280 --> 09:12.690
[Making guests feel at home]

09:07.870 --> 09:09.800
and conduct regular assessments.

09:12.200 --> 09:15.510
Three receptionists must be on duty
during off-peak hours.

09:15.510 --> 09:17.360
Other on-duty staff
should make full use of their time

09:15.980 --> 09:22.070
[Convenience Handbook]

09:17.600 --> 09:19.200
to improve foreign language skills

09:19.200 --> 09:20.960
and familiarize themselves
with information around the hotel.

09:20.960 --> 09:24.090
On-duty staff must keep
hospitality etiquette in mind.

09:24.210 --> 09:26.670
Phones must be answered
within three rings.

09:27.440 --> 09:29.500
Hello, Purong Hotel at your service.

09:30.710 --> 09:31.470
Yes, we do.

09:34.830 --> 09:36.290
The logistics department

09:36.520 --> 09:41.120
is responsible for restoring Purong's
tradition of displaying jasmine flowers.

09:51.390 --> 09:54.240
All areas must ensure to always provide

09:54.240 --> 09:56.190
the best all-around experience for guests,

09:56.190 --> 09:59.650
including visual, olfactory,
auditory, and tactile senses.

10:25.960 --> 10:27.840
I hope everyone in the hotel
works together.

10:27.840 --> 10:29.940
Let's bring back the original intention
of making guests feel at home

10:29.940 --> 10:30.910
to Purong.

10:37.440 --> 10:39.240
Jia, are you done with your work?

10:40.150 --> 10:42.150
The guests in rooms 16, 17, and 18
have checked out.

10:42.150 --> 10:43.320
Go and clean them up.

10:45.080 --> 10:46.440
I have a headache.

10:46.600 --> 10:48.120
I think I'm sick.

10:48.250 --> 10:49.370
Find someone else.

10:55.790 --> 10:56.390
Yin Xiang.

10:56.390 --> 10:57.750
Stop right there, Miyu.

10:58.240 --> 11:00.040
I still have a bunch of work to do.

11:00.390 --> 11:02.000
You can't just exploit me

11:02.000 --> 11:03.600
because we're on good terms.

11:07.440 --> 11:09.320
Is anyone else free right now?

11:25.600 --> 11:26.270
Jia,

11:28.870 --> 11:30.150
if you're not feeling well,

11:30.150 --> 11:31.320
go see a doctor.

11:31.510 --> 11:32.360
Bring back a doctor's note,

11:32.360 --> 11:34.000
and I'll let you go home to rest.

11:34.000 --> 11:34.910
Go now.

11:36.510 --> 11:37.950
I got my period,

11:38.030 --> 11:39.230
and my stomach hurts.

11:40.750 --> 11:42.200
You got your period twice in half a month?

11:42.200 --> 11:43.120
Are you okay?

11:45.020 --> 11:46.440
Health is the most important thing.

11:46.440 --> 11:47.510
If your body

11:47.510 --> 11:49.510
can't handle the current workload,

11:49.910 --> 11:50.550
that's okay.

11:50.550 --> 11:51.630
Don't push yourself.

11:51.630 --> 11:53.080
I'll help you talk to HR.

11:54.120 --> 11:54.910
No need.

11:55.000 --> 11:56.260
It's not that serious.

11:56.790 --> 11:58.150
I feel much better now.

11:59.200 --> 12:00.200
Glad to hear that.

12:00.440 --> 12:01.500
If you can manage,

12:01.600 --> 12:03.660
I'll still leave 16, 17, and 18 to you.

12:10.030 --> 12:11.240
What's going on today?

12:11.240 --> 12:13.170
Why isn't she buying this anymore?

12:36.600 --> 12:37.660
What are you doing?

12:38.270 --> 12:39.720
You startled me!

12:40.840 --> 12:42.050
I wasn't doing anything.

12:42.050 --> 12:43.750
How could you just go through
a guest's things?

12:43.750 --> 12:44.670
I was just looking.

12:44.670 --> 12:45.790
I didn't take anything.

12:45.790 --> 12:46.550
Besides,

12:46.550 --> 12:48.360
this guest's belongings
are scattered everywhere.

12:48.360 --> 12:49.840
How am I supposed to clean up
if I can't touch them?

12:49.840 --> 12:51.200
Is this what you call cleaning up?

12:51.200 --> 12:53.660
You cleaned them
right into the guest's bag.

12:59.360 --> 13:00.360
Is this fine now?

13:00.750 --> 13:01.910
Jia, let me tell you,

13:02.150 --> 13:03.440
don't push your luck

13:03.440 --> 13:05.140
to do these borderline things.

13:05.140 --> 13:06.270
If something goes wrong,

13:06.270 --> 13:09.130
you won't even be able to
explain yourself clearly.

13:13.930 --> 13:15.750
I haven't finished yet.

13:15.750 --> 13:17.360
Are you done?

13:17.360 --> 13:19.550
You've been targeting me since morning!

13:19.550 --> 13:20.670
Don't bully me too much!

13:20.670 --> 13:22.370
I should be the one saying that.

13:22.370 --> 13:23.560
Let me tell you, Jia.

13:23.790 --> 13:25.870
It's fine if you have a problem with me.

13:25.870 --> 13:27.000
But as an attendant,

13:27.000 --> 13:28.790
you lead the other attendants

13:28.790 --> 13:29.670
to slack off.

13:29.670 --> 13:30.800
Isn't this too much?

13:31.440 --> 13:32.030
Also,

13:32.110 --> 13:32.990
please remember,

13:32.990 --> 13:33.910
I am your forewoman,

13:33.910 --> 13:34.840
not your enemy.

13:34.980 --> 13:36.270
I just checked Room 1818,

13:36.270 --> 13:37.390
which you are responsible for.

13:37.390 --> 13:38.600
It's not cleaned up to standard.

13:38.600 --> 13:40.150
After you finish cleaning this room,

13:40.150 --> 13:41.480
go clean that one again.

13:41.720 --> 13:43.330
Who are you trying to scare?

13:43.440 --> 13:45.040
Aren't you just a forewoman?

13:45.510 --> 13:47.670
So what if you're good at currying favor
with management?

13:47.670 --> 13:48.530
Let me tell you,

13:48.750 --> 13:50.880
if you want it cleaned, do it yourself.

14:05.440 --> 14:06.360
Ms. Xu,

14:07.120 --> 14:08.790
can you carry it alone?

14:09.140 --> 14:09.970
Yes, I can.

14:10.870 --> 14:11.320
Hello.

14:11.630 --> 14:12.390
Hello, sir.

14:12.390 --> 14:13.440
Welcome to Purong Hotel.

14:12.640 --> 14:13.990
[Passport]

14:13.440 --> 14:14.640
I have a reservation.

14:15.540 --> 14:16.670
Excuse me, I was wondering

14:16.670 --> 14:17.960
if Amber Santos' installation exhibition

14:17.960 --> 14:19.000
is around here?

14:19.860 --> 14:21.190
Please wait a moment, sir.

14:21.190 --> 14:22.400
[Convenience Handbook]

14:27.910 --> 14:29.150
I'm sorry, sir.

14:29.170 --> 14:30.300
I don't really know.

14:30.320 --> 14:31.480
It's fine.

14:32.110 --> 14:33.510
Are you looking for Amber Santos's

14:33.510 --> 14:34.650
Four Seasons Art Exhibition?

14:34.650 --> 14:35.640
Yes, that's the one.

14:35.640 --> 14:37.440
This exhibition is indeed hard to find.

14:37.440 --> 14:38.790
It's in the art space on the eighth floor

14:38.790 --> 14:40.010
of the mall next door.

14:40.220 --> 14:41.440
There are posters up there.

14:41.440 --> 14:42.600
You'll see them when you get up there.

14:42.600 --> 14:43.870
Just follow the directions.

14:43.870 --> 14:44.360
Okay, okay.

14:44.360 --> 14:45.200
I've asked quite a few people,

14:45.200 --> 14:45.720
and no one seems to know.

14:45.720 --> 14:46.910
This exhibition just opened in Shanghai,

14:46.910 --> 14:48.390
so it's normal that many people
don't know about it yet.

14:48.390 --> 14:51.000
But it should close at 7:30.

14:51.000 --> 14:51.750
Keep an eye on the time.

14:51.750 --> 14:52.550
Don't miss it.

14:52.550 --> 14:53.870
Okay, okay. Thank you.

14:53.870 --> 14:54.750
Glad to serve you.

14:54.750 --> 14:55.680
Okay, thank you.

15:01.630 --> 15:03.290
Sir, it's done.

15:03.600 --> 15:05.260
-Thank you.
-Enjoy your stay.

15:10.240 --> 15:10.720
Come in.

15:13.670 --> 15:15.490
Mr. Ji, the finance department
is here to report the accounts.

15:15.490 --> 15:16.330
Let them in.

15:16.390 --> 15:17.190
Okay, come in.

15:26.270 --> 15:27.080
Hello, Mr. Ji.

15:27.200 --> 15:28.750
I am the accounting manager
of the finance department.

15:28.750 --> 15:29.620
My name is Gao Fan.

15:29.620 --> 15:30.910
We received a notice this morning

15:30.910 --> 15:32.360
saying that you want to
check the accounts personally.

15:32.360 --> 15:32.870
So,

15:32.910 --> 15:34.320
we dug out these ledgers

15:34.320 --> 15:36.550
for you from the warehouse.

15:37.000 --> 15:37.750
However,

15:37.750 --> 15:39.720
there's a lot of dust on them,

15:39.720 --> 15:40.840
and the paper is quite brittle.

15:40.840 --> 15:42.080
When you flip through them later,

15:42.080 --> 15:43.410
please be very careful.

15:44.010 --> 15:45.340
Where is your director?

15:45.440 --> 15:46.840
You mean Director Huang?

15:47.040 --> 15:50.160
He went out early this morning
with Mr. Wei to handle some business.

15:50.160 --> 15:52.150
He handed these matters over to me.

15:53.440 --> 15:54.120
Look here.

15:54.910 --> 15:55.790
This cart

15:55.790 --> 15:58.660
mainly contains details of supply amounts,

15:59.200 --> 16:01.240
such as raw materials, consumables,

16:01.240 --> 16:03.600
semi-finished products,
and warehouse goods.

16:03.600 --> 16:04.150
You can

16:04.150 --> 16:05.550
look through these freely.

16:05.550 --> 16:06.300
This cart

16:06.670 --> 16:07.790
is all about

16:08.080 --> 16:10.480
operating expenses and production costs.

16:10.500 --> 16:12.440
This cart is a bit messy.

16:12.630 --> 16:14.440
It mainly contains

16:14.440 --> 16:16.790
detailed ledgers of fixed assets,

16:16.790 --> 16:19.030
three-column subsidiary ledgers
for borrowing, lending, and balance,

16:19.030 --> 16:20.910
and employee salary accounts.

16:20.910 --> 16:21.770
That's enough.

16:23.440 --> 16:26.460
Then I'll trouble you
to review them personally, Mr. Ji.

16:26.460 --> 16:27.000
Okay.

16:36.030 --> 16:36.550
Mr. Gao,

16:36.770 --> 16:38.590
did you see Mr. Ji's face?

16:39.440 --> 16:40.600
With all those carts of stuff,

16:40.600 --> 16:41.960
if he doesn't get dizzy looking at them,

16:41.960 --> 16:44.090
he'll at least get a dust mite allergy.

16:44.630 --> 16:45.840
Didn't he want to investigate?

16:45.840 --> 16:47.080
Let him.

16:47.910 --> 16:50.520
Take his time to investigate it.

16:55.240 --> 16:56.600
Why did you think of

16:56.600 --> 16:57.840
treating me to barbecue today?

16:57.840 --> 16:59.040
I just care about you.

17:00.240 --> 17:01.510
How's the audit going?

17:02.030 --> 17:02.960
As for the audit,

17:03.270 --> 17:04.470
I originally thought

17:04.750 --> 17:06.400
following the supply of linens

17:06.400 --> 17:07.829
and cleaning fees

17:08.310 --> 17:10.200
could reveal some discrepancies.

17:10.200 --> 17:11.930
But the accounts are balanced,

17:12.349 --> 17:13.430
the receipts are complete,

17:13.430 --> 17:14.440
and there are no loopholes.

17:14.440 --> 17:16.670
The finance department
is like a spider's web.

17:16.670 --> 17:18.790
They won't let someone who just arrived

17:18.790 --> 17:20.190
find any flaws so easily.

17:22.790 --> 17:23.510
Rui,

17:25.240 --> 17:27.310
stay and work with me.

17:27.310 --> 17:28.270
Help me.

17:36.440 --> 17:38.300
You think I'm not sincere enough?

17:39.830 --> 17:40.350
Come on.

17:46.990 --> 17:47.610
Ji Feng,

17:47.640 --> 17:48.500
stop drinking.

17:49.240 --> 17:49.970
Listen to me.

17:54.000 --> 17:55.800
Actually, at this dinner today,

17:57.850 --> 17:59.180
I'm here to say goodbye.

18:00.840 --> 18:02.440
I've already made arrangements

18:02.440 --> 18:05.080
to go to Guilin
to be a financial director.

18:08.010 --> 18:08.720
By the way,

18:09.270 --> 18:10.130
before I leave,

18:11.110 --> 18:12.240
I have a gift for you.

18:12.510 --> 18:13.590
I hope it's useful.

18:23.130 --> 18:26.660
This is the account book I kept
when I was the head of accounting.

18:26.930 --> 18:28.020
[F&B Department]

18:28.040 --> 18:28.710
[Handled by: Manager Chen]
[Handled by: Manager Jia]

18:30.720 --> 18:31.780
The real accounts.

18:38.590 --> 18:39.980
Later, they found out.

18:40.790 --> 18:43.550
My career hit the ceiling.

18:43.760 --> 18:45.760
Now I am the daily audit supervisor.

18:46.000 --> 18:48.420
But honestly I'm just a nobody

18:48.450 --> 18:50.110
drifting around in the finance department.

18:50.110 --> 18:52.110
I can understand how you feel.

18:52.660 --> 18:54.320
I've endured for so many years

18:54.790 --> 18:56.720
and my skills are completely gone.

18:57.590 --> 18:59.320
I can't help you with anything.

18:59.650 --> 19:01.790
The little useful information I have left

19:01.790 --> 19:03.190
has all been given to you.

19:08.570 --> 19:09.220
Rui,

19:10.030 --> 19:10.880
here's to you.

19:11.520 --> 19:13.390
May your career take off

19:13.410 --> 19:14.940
and everything go your way.

19:27.680 --> 19:28.400
Ji Feng,

19:29.240 --> 19:31.620
I'm ashamed

19:31.650 --> 19:34.110
I left you behind
to handle everything alone

19:34.110 --> 19:35.840
while I ran off like a deserter.

19:36.160 --> 19:37.920
I'll drink three glasses as a penalty.

19:37.920 --> 19:38.440
Rui,

19:38.860 --> 19:40.050
you don't owe me anything.

19:40.050 --> 19:40.960
You have your future,

19:40.960 --> 19:42.160
and I have my challenges.

19:42.160 --> 19:43.890
We are going our separate ways.

19:44.180 --> 19:44.930
It's just a pity.

19:44.930 --> 19:45.930
Why feel guilty?

19:46.520 --> 19:47.480
No matter what,

19:47.500 --> 19:48.890
seeing you find your place

19:48.890 --> 19:50.240
makes me happy.

19:50.330 --> 19:50.940
Really.

19:54.790 --> 19:55.680
Cheers.

20:03.690 --> 20:05.530
Mr. Tan, time for your medicine.

20:07.650 --> 20:08.790
What do you always call me

20:08.790 --> 20:09.830
"Mr. Tan"?

20:09.830 --> 20:11.290
Call me Daniel from now on.

20:11.620 --> 20:13.450
You're making me sound old.

20:13.970 --> 20:15.540
Daniel, here you go.

20:16.670 --> 20:17.800
Just leave it there.

20:18.830 --> 20:21.160
You still have to take it
if I leave it here.

20:21.930 --> 20:23.530
You can't skip a single dose.

20:24.880 --> 20:27.280
You don't want to
take your medicine again?

20:27.510 --> 20:28.200
Fine.

20:28.310 --> 20:30.180
I'll call Jizhou right now

20:30.270 --> 20:31.730
and have him take you back.

20:31.750 --> 20:33.320
Eat, eat, eat.

20:36.200 --> 20:37.200
Don't ever mention

20:37.200 --> 20:38.770
Jizhou taking me back again.

20:38.770 --> 20:39.750
Swallow it.

20:45.240 --> 20:47.140
Do you often meet guests like this?

20:47.140 --> 20:48.140
So disobedient.

20:48.270 --> 20:48.960
No.

20:49.240 --> 20:51.300
Mr. Tan is very easy to get along with.

20:52.930 --> 20:56.290
Are you busy on the executive floor?

20:56.320 --> 20:58.940
Is the forewoman job going well?

20:59.530 --> 21:00.920
I'm working very well here.

21:00.920 --> 21:01.920
Thank you.

21:02.440 --> 21:03.240
You guys talk.

21:03.240 --> 21:04.070
I'll get going.

21:04.070 --> 21:04.440
Okay.

21:04.440 --> 21:05.030
Okay.

21:08.610 --> 21:09.780
Good girl.

21:13.170 --> 21:14.130
We meet again.

21:14.160 --> 21:15.050
It's you?

21:15.680 --> 21:16.830
I'm looking for Daniel.

21:16.830 --> 21:18.270
I'm Tan Jiaming, his son.

21:19.220 --> 21:19.800
Come in.

21:20.830 --> 21:21.590
Why are you here?

21:21.590 --> 21:23.080
Auntie Wanjun is here too.

21:28.350 --> 21:29.110
Ms. Xu.

21:31.620 --> 21:32.390
Thank you.

21:33.030 --> 21:34.690
This exhibition is very nice.

21:35.260 --> 21:36.440
But what I'm more grateful for is

21:36.440 --> 21:37.790
that you saved my father's life.

21:37.790 --> 21:40.250
So this is a little token
of my appreciation.

21:40.350 --> 21:41.680
I hope you can accept it.

21:42.940 --> 21:44.130
[Amber Santos Four Seasons Art Exhibition]

21:43.240 --> 21:44.090
I can't accept it.

21:44.090 --> 21:45.950
No, you must accept it.

21:45.980 --> 21:47.400
I am really grateful to you.

21:47.400 --> 21:49.440
I've never seen my father so happy.

21:49.440 --> 21:50.700
It's all thanks to you.

21:51.960 --> 21:52.860
Mr. Tan,

21:52.960 --> 21:54.070
I appreciate your kindness,

21:54.070 --> 21:56.070
But I really can't accept the gift.

21:56.070 --> 21:58.070
If you are really satisfied with
my service,

21:58.070 --> 22:01.070
then you are welcome to
visit Purong Hotel more often.

22:01.830 --> 22:02.830
All right.

22:03.400 --> 22:04.350
Ms. Xu,

22:05.160 --> 22:06.620
you're really different.

22:07.440 --> 22:08.160
Here's the thing.

22:08.160 --> 22:09.440
When I chat with my father,

22:09.440 --> 22:10.700
he often mentions you.

22:11.000 --> 22:12.510
He said "Ms. Xu who takes care of me

22:12.510 --> 22:15.200
studied hotel management,

22:15.200 --> 22:17.270
but she has a great sense of art.

22:17.270 --> 22:19.130
It's a pleasure to talk with her."

22:19.590 --> 22:20.850
Seeing you today,

22:21.720 --> 22:23.160
I can see that's true.

22:24.270 --> 22:25.070
Thank you.

22:25.270 --> 22:27.110
Ms. Xu, can I ask you a question?

22:27.590 --> 22:30.680
Why do you work as an attendant at Purong?

22:31.570 --> 22:32.300
I...

22:32.430 --> 22:34.630
I'm not trying to pry into your privacy.

22:34.720 --> 22:35.790
It's like this.

22:35.790 --> 22:39.270
I think with your knowledge and ability,

22:39.440 --> 22:41.920
you should go to a bigger platform

22:41.920 --> 22:44.850
to do work that better reflects
your personal value.

22:46.560 --> 22:47.350
So,

22:51.440 --> 22:53.680
this is my name card.

22:54.110 --> 22:55.270
If you need it,

22:55.130 --> 22:57.050
[Curator, Tan Jizhou]

22:55.270 --> 22:56.720
I can help you find work

22:56.720 --> 22:58.270
related to the arts,

22:58.270 --> 23:00.310
and I'd be willing to
recommend you as well.

23:00.310 --> 23:01.720
You are a curator?

23:02.030 --> 23:03.270
That's amazing.

23:03.920 --> 23:04.830
Do you know me?

23:06.240 --> 23:08.240
Then I guess I'm not amazing enough.

23:11.240 --> 23:12.610
Well, Mr. Tan,

23:12.640 --> 23:14.440
thank you for acknowledging me.

23:15.240 --> 23:16.230
But I currently have no plans

23:16.230 --> 23:17.590
to leave Purong.

23:18.070 --> 23:19.200
Because I think

23:19.200 --> 23:21.400
being able to provide
every guest away from home

23:21.400 --> 23:23.440
with a service that feels like home

23:23.440 --> 23:25.330
is a very valuable thing.

23:25.440 --> 23:28.310
So I really love my current job.

23:30.880 --> 23:31.350
Okay.

23:31.790 --> 23:32.590
I understand.

23:32.850 --> 23:33.680
If you need anything,

23:33.680 --> 23:35.210
you can contact me anytime.

23:35.790 --> 23:36.510
Thank you.

23:36.510 --> 23:37.640
Mr. Tan, good night.

23:37.640 --> 23:38.590
Good night.

23:52.070 --> 23:52.920
Mr. Ji.

23:53.400 --> 23:54.030
You...

23:54.750 --> 23:55.680
What's wrong with you?

23:55.680 --> 23:56.200
Nothing.

23:56.200 --> 23:57.600
I just had a little drink.

24:03.860 --> 24:04.900
Are you okay?

24:05.230 --> 24:05.990
I'm fine.

24:12.270 --> 24:13.200
I have the room card.

24:13.200 --> 24:14.460
Let me swipe it for you.

24:18.510 --> 24:19.370
Please come in.

24:47.880 --> 24:48.750
Xu Miyu,

24:49.790 --> 24:50.790
thank you

24:52.130 --> 24:52.960
for staying.

24:59.680 --> 25:00.550
Sorry.

25:01.030 --> 25:01.720
Sorry.

25:03.110 --> 25:03.710
It's okay.

25:04.240 --> 25:04.840
It's okay.

25:05.670 --> 25:06.530
I can handle it.

25:07.750 --> 25:08.610
I can handle it.

25:09.150 --> 25:10.180
Thank you.

25:39.660 --> 25:42.930
[Zhao Ning – 19th Floor, Rest]
[He Xiao – 19th Floor, Night Shift]

25:39.830 --> 25:40.440
Ms. Xu.

25:40.440 --> 25:41.640
Ms. Xu, are you there?

25:44.070 --> 25:44.510
Yes.

25:45.110 --> 25:45.790
Come quickly.

25:45.790 --> 25:47.350
Jia has been held up by the guest

25:47.350 --> 25:48.110
in room 1817.

25:48.800 --> 25:49.460
I'm coming.

25:52.640 --> 25:53.200
Ke Wenxue,

25:53.200 --> 25:55.440
do you have the information
of the guest in room 1817?

25:55.440 --> 25:57.030
She's a middle-aged female guest.

25:57.030 --> 25:59.760
It seems she was upgraded
from the regular floor.

26:00.880 --> 26:02.080
Okay, got it, thanks.

26:05.880 --> 26:06.920
Hello, sorry to bother you.

26:06.920 --> 26:07.920
I am the forewoman of the executive floor.

26:07.920 --> 26:09.030
May I come in?

26:09.030 --> 26:09.680
Come in!

26:12.960 --> 26:13.590
Hello.

26:13.810 --> 26:14.590
Sorry.

26:14.590 --> 26:16.150
We have received your complaint.

26:16.150 --> 26:17.510
I'm here to understand the situation.

26:17.510 --> 26:18.310
Ask her.

26:19.110 --> 26:20.270
I didn't take it.

26:20.270 --> 26:21.550
You're lying!

26:21.680 --> 26:23.400
Hand over my diamond ring right now!

26:23.400 --> 26:25.070
I didn't take her diamond ring.

26:25.070 --> 26:26.460
I really didn't!

26:27.750 --> 26:28.350
Excuse me.

26:28.510 --> 26:29.750
I am the general manager here.

26:29.750 --> 26:30.640
May I come in?

26:31.000 --> 26:31.510
Come in.

26:49.790 --> 26:50.920
This customer said

26:50.920 --> 26:52.270
she lost a diamond ring in her room.

26:52.270 --> 26:53.550
She took it!

26:53.550 --> 26:56.030
Look at how sneaky she is.

26:56.030 --> 26:58.030
You were about to run
as soon as I walked in.

26:58.030 --> 26:59.030
Why did you run?

26:59.030 --> 27:01.750
I had just finished cleaning the room
and was about to leave.

27:01.750 --> 27:03.810
Have you finished cleaning the room?

27:03.830 --> 27:05.720
Have you made the bed?

27:06.400 --> 27:08.160
You even left your rag in the room.

27:08.160 --> 27:09.270
If you didn't do anything wrong,

27:09.270 --> 27:10.590
why were you panicking?

27:10.590 --> 27:11.920
When I entered the room,

27:11.920 --> 27:13.270
I lost my diamond ring.

27:13.590 --> 27:14.920
Please calm down first.

27:14.920 --> 27:16.590
We will investigate this thoroughly,

27:16.590 --> 27:17.440
and then...

27:21.310 --> 27:22.030
Mr. Ji.

27:22.030 --> 27:23.830
I have really checked this room.

27:27.240 --> 27:28.300
Madam, I apologize

27:28.350 --> 27:30.210
for your unpleasant experience.

27:30.310 --> 27:32.480
May I ask how long
after the attendant left

27:32.480 --> 27:33.680
did you call her back?

27:33.750 --> 27:34.790
As soon as I noticed something
wrong with her,

27:34.790 --> 27:35.940
I checked my bag.

27:36.160 --> 27:38.070
The diamond ring was indeed missing,

27:38.070 --> 27:39.510
so I went out to find her immediately.

27:39.510 --> 27:40.880
Hand it over right now.

27:40.880 --> 27:42.590
I didn't take it.

27:44.440 --> 27:45.030
Jia,

27:45.110 --> 27:46.510
come in and check with me.

27:52.620 --> 27:54.020
Excuse me, wait a moment.

27:58.440 --> 27:59.270
Alright.

28:00.350 --> 28:01.310
Let me ask you,

28:01.720 --> 28:04.110
did you take
the guest's belongings or not?

28:04.110 --> 28:05.310
If you don't tell me the truth,

28:05.310 --> 28:06.640
I really can't help you.

28:14.110 --> 28:15.720
I was just curious

28:16.340 --> 28:19.060
and searched the price online.

28:16.450 --> 28:17.340
[Moissanite Ring – 18K Gold Engagement
Diamond Ring, High-End Replica Ring]

28:17.370 --> 28:18.000
[True Love Lab-Grown Gemstone Ring]

28:18.020 --> 28:18.910
[High-Quality 18K Gold
Six-Prong Lab Diamond Ring]

28:19.440 --> 28:21.900
You rummaged through
the guest's bag again?

28:22.030 --> 28:22.550
Okay.

28:23.030 --> 28:24.440
Come with me and turn yourself in.

28:24.440 --> 28:25.170
Sister Miyu,

28:25.270 --> 28:25.720
I was wrong.

28:25.720 --> 28:26.780
I really was wrong.

28:26.880 --> 28:28.810
Please, listen to my explanation.

28:29.160 --> 28:30.030
I thought

28:30.680 --> 28:32.180
it was just a small matter.

29:15.420 --> 29:15.860
[Search for Similar Items]

29:15.880 --> 29:17.580
[Moissanite–
Birthday Gift for Girlfriend]

29:16.920 --> 29:18.030
I wouldn't want it

29:17.600 --> 29:18.540
[S990 sterling silver little snake ring]

29:18.560 --> 29:19.280
[Minimalist sterling silver tail ring
for men and women]

29:18.750 --> 29:20.510
even if she gave it to me.

29:21.960 --> 29:23.720
I knew it was a fake.

29:24.440 --> 29:26.570
But it was just such a coincidence.

29:28.350 --> 29:29.410
What are you doing?

29:29.510 --> 29:30.310
Not making a sound,

29:30.310 --> 29:30.830
you scared me!

29:30.830 --> 29:32.590
Sorry. Sorry.

29:38.160 --> 29:39.680
I realized right then
that something was wrong.

29:39.680 --> 29:41.000
Fortunately, I caught her.

29:41.000 --> 29:41.510
I...

29:44.490 --> 29:45.920
Our staff will be right here.

29:45.920 --> 29:47.550
Please wait a moment.

29:50.070 --> 29:51.030
It's over.

29:51.960 --> 29:53.680
She's going to get sued.

29:53.720 --> 29:54.650
She deserves it.

29:54.830 --> 29:57.080
If she's got sticky fingers,
she shouldn't be working as an attendant.

29:57.080 --> 29:58.590
Is this your first day knowing Jia?

29:58.590 --> 30:00.600
She only acts tough on the outside.

30:00.830 --> 30:02.760
She doesn't have the guts to steal.

30:03.030 --> 30:04.800
How long do I have to wait?

30:05.030 --> 30:06.160
Can you hurry up?

30:06.830 --> 30:07.680
I don't know if our forewoman

30:07.680 --> 30:08.980
can settle this.

30:09.270 --> 30:11.790
Jia and Ms. Xu fell out a long time ago.

30:12.440 --> 30:14.950
I'm afraid no one can save her this time.

30:15.070 --> 30:18.060
It's hard to say if Ms. Xu
can even save herself.

30:18.440 --> 30:19.510
Mr. Ji just took office,

30:19.510 --> 30:21.440
and this scandal
happens on the executive floor.

30:21.440 --> 30:23.500
This is a huge embarrassment for him.

30:25.030 --> 30:28.600
Even with Ms. Xu‘s strong backing,

30:29.030 --> 30:30.070
she probably won't

30:30.070 --> 30:31.600
escape the blame this time.

30:33.830 --> 30:34.440
Stop looking.

30:34.440 --> 30:35.070
Excuse me.

30:44.110 --> 30:46.370
You can't just favor your own employees.

30:47.310 --> 30:48.550
I told you she took it.

30:48.550 --> 30:50.240
Why do you insist on searching the room?

30:50.240 --> 30:50.920
Ma'am,

30:50.920 --> 30:52.400
the situation is still unclear.

30:52.400 --> 30:54.000
It might just be a misunderstanding.

30:54.000 --> 30:55.730
What's wrong with this toilet?

30:57.550 --> 30:58.640
Dare.

30:59.310 --> 31:00.720
This toilet has been clogged for ages.

31:00.720 --> 31:02.380
The water won't go down at all.

31:03.460 --> 31:04.160
What are you doing?

31:04.160 --> 31:05.110
I asked you to find my stuff.

31:05.110 --> 31:06.590
Why are you plunging the toilet?

31:06.590 --> 31:07.160
Go.

31:17.750 --> 31:19.270
Mr. Ji, the security footage
you asked for is ready.

31:19.270 --> 31:21.000
Mr. Ji, we didn't find the ring.

31:21.590 --> 31:22.270
Okay.

31:23.590 --> 31:24.200
Ma'am,

31:24.220 --> 31:25.490
I need to go to the surveillance room.

31:25.490 --> 31:26.960
You can't just leave.

31:26.960 --> 31:28.440
Are you trying to stall me?

31:28.550 --> 31:30.370
Get this straight.

31:30.440 --> 31:32.790
I'm making things easier for you now.

31:33.570 --> 31:35.110
Problems that can be solved with money

31:35.110 --> 31:36.160
aren't really problems,

31:36.160 --> 31:36.590
right?

31:36.750 --> 31:38.920
I didn't want to
make a big deal out of this.

31:38.920 --> 31:41.350
It's very bad for your hotel's image.

31:41.350 --> 31:43.810
But if you insist on
beating around the bush,

31:44.270 --> 31:45.870
I'll have to call the police.

31:46.600 --> 31:47.590
Two hours.

31:47.590 --> 31:49.110
Give us another two hours.

31:49.110 --> 31:50.160
We will definitely find it.

31:50.160 --> 31:51.110
I don't have two hours.

31:51.110 --> 31:52.110
I'm checking out.

31:52.270 --> 31:53.110
One hour.

31:55.240 --> 31:55.790
Alright.

31:56.240 --> 31:57.040
Just one hour.

31:59.810 --> 32:02.200
[Notice of calling the fire police]

32:08.000 --> 32:08.550
Mr. Ji.

32:10.750 --> 32:11.770
Instead of looking for the ring,

32:11.770 --> 32:12.590
why are you following me?

32:12.590 --> 32:13.790
That ring is fake.

32:14.880 --> 32:15.480
Evidence.

32:15.770 --> 32:16.640
Jia...

32:18.550 --> 32:21.030
I judged from the guest's attitude.

32:21.440 --> 32:23.310
Normally, if someone loses
something so valuable,

32:23.310 --> 32:25.640
they would want to know the truth

32:26.030 --> 32:28.360
instead of just asking for compensation.

32:28.590 --> 32:29.350
However,

32:29.440 --> 32:31.720
a 100,000 yuan ring disappears,

32:31.720 --> 32:33.720
and she doesn't care how it got lost.

32:33.790 --> 32:36.000
She just opens her mouth
and asks for money.

32:36.000 --> 32:37.270
I think it's very suspicious.

32:37.270 --> 32:40.670
At a time like this,
you're still trying to shield your staff.

32:45.960 --> 32:48.320
When you run into a guest
who frames you like this,

32:48.320 --> 32:49.530
the only solution is…

32:49.560 --> 32:51.640
To find what she's hiding.

32:54.640 --> 32:55.900
You have 50 minutes left.

32:55.900 --> 32:57.440
If you can't find the ring, you pay.

32:57.440 --> 32:57.960
Me?

33:01.240 --> 33:03.440
Why should I pay?

33:07.180 --> 33:07.920
What are you doing?

33:07.920 --> 33:08.830
I told you to look for something.

33:08.830 --> 33:10.690
Why are you digging in the toilet?

33:12.880 --> 33:14.920
You all know how much

33:14.920 --> 33:16.450
a one-carat diamond costs.

33:16.640 --> 33:18.960
A random brand costs over 100,000.

33:18.960 --> 33:20.640
I won't argue with you.

33:20.640 --> 33:21.680
Let's round it off

33:21.680 --> 33:23.120
and just pay me 100,000.

33:23.150 --> 33:25.400
Now you're the ones making trouble for me?

33:25.400 --> 33:26.880
What terrible luck.

33:27.030 --> 33:28.440
I'm going to the lobby to check out.

33:28.440 --> 33:30.240
Call your general manager here!

33:30.830 --> 33:31.590
Ma'am.

33:33.350 --> 33:34.110
What are you doing?

33:34.110 --> 33:35.000
I'm checking out.

33:35.000 --> 33:35.720
Ma'am,

33:35.720 --> 33:37.350
your ring hasn't been found yet, right?

33:37.350 --> 33:38.720
I brought a professional here

33:38.720 --> 33:39.680
to help you look for it.

33:39.680 --> 33:41.240
Please give us two more minutes.

33:41.240 --> 33:41.960
You look for it.

33:41.960 --> 33:42.790
I'm leaving.

33:43.030 --> 33:44.160
This way, please.

33:44.160 --> 33:44.880
Okay.

33:46.450 --> 33:47.560
What are you doing?

33:53.070 --> 33:53.880
Miss.

33:54.710 --> 33:56.150
I can't take this toilet apart.

33:56.150 --> 33:57.720
They were all installed
by the manufacturer.

33:57.720 --> 34:00.070
If you want it removed,
the Engineering Department
has to follow the procedure.

34:00.070 --> 34:02.270
I can fill out any paperwork
you need later.

34:02.270 --> 34:03.960
Can we just fix this emergency first?

34:03.960 --> 34:05.000
No.

34:05.270 --> 34:07.470
Call me when you have all the paperwork.

34:07.750 --> 34:09.710
All talk and no action again.

34:09.710 --> 34:10.440
Does your hotel

34:10.440 --> 34:12.710
only play these childish games?

34:13.750 --> 34:14.400
Excuse me.

34:14.400 --> 34:15.330
Coming through.

34:17.960 --> 34:19.230
Rumors like people saying you got here

34:19.230 --> 34:22.280
through connections
aren't entirely a bad thing.

34:22.630 --> 34:26.090
If you handled well, they can actually
work to your advantage.

34:27.170 --> 34:27.909
Sir.

34:28.020 --> 34:29.159
Wait a moment.

34:29.510 --> 34:30.110
What is it?

34:31.030 --> 34:32.090
Don't you know me?

34:32.320 --> 34:33.360
I'm the new forewoman

34:33.360 --> 34:35.150
promoted by Mr. Ji.

34:35.570 --> 34:37.739
If you want to follow the procedure,

34:37.770 --> 34:38.840
how about this?

34:38.840 --> 34:40.239
I'll call him right now

34:40.270 --> 34:43.000
and have him personally
do the paperwork for you?

34:48.320 --> 34:49.440
Okay, okay.

35:09.840 --> 35:10.970
It's disassembled.

35:11.150 --> 35:12.010
If you're done,

35:12.360 --> 35:13.020
you call me.

35:26.110 --> 35:26.670
Ms. Wang,

35:26.750 --> 35:29.030
-please wait outside.
-I'm just looking.

35:29.030 --> 35:30.190
It smells bad here.

35:30.630 --> 35:31.890
Sorry for the trouble.

35:53.070 --> 35:53.870
I've found it.

35:59.030 --> 36:00.400
This is a valuable item.

36:00.400 --> 36:02.110
Our hotel needs to go through
an appraisal process.

36:02.110 --> 36:03.000
Please wait a moment.

36:03.000 --> 36:03.670
Appraisal?

36:06.230 --> 36:06.910
Mr. Zhu,

36:06.960 --> 36:08.090
are you almost here?

36:08.200 --> 36:09.320
There's no need for an appraisal.

36:09.320 --> 36:10.150
Why go through all that trouble?

36:10.150 --> 36:11.080
No need, no need.

36:11.760 --> 36:12.590
Are you sure?

36:13.030 --> 36:15.920
This is a diamond ring worth over 100,000.

36:15.920 --> 36:18.580
Our hotel absolutely
cannot take this lightly.

36:18.760 --> 36:19.360
I'm sure.

36:19.840 --> 36:20.770
What appraisal?

36:20.920 --> 36:22.250
You are so much trouble.

36:22.670 --> 36:25.000
Is there anything else
I can help you with?

36:25.280 --> 36:26.920
We look forward to seeing you again
at Purong Hotel.

36:26.920 --> 36:29.070
We are always at your service!

36:36.840 --> 36:37.610
Mr. Ji,

36:37.850 --> 36:39.450
drink some more honey water,

36:39.500 --> 36:42.110
and eat some apples
and oranges to sober up.

36:45.180 --> 36:46.100
Thank you.

36:46.860 --> 36:48.030
About that jewelry appraisal...

36:48.030 --> 36:49.400
There's no jewelry appraisal.

36:49.400 --> 36:50.530
I was bluffing.

36:50.550 --> 36:51.840
She knew her stuff was fake,

36:51.840 --> 36:53.770
so she wouldn't dare to drag it out.

37:08.280 --> 37:09.320
Miyu,

37:11.070 --> 37:12.030
I'm sorry.

37:13.670 --> 37:14.630
Thank you.

37:18.760 --> 37:19.440
All right.

37:22.150 --> 37:23.540
Just learn your lesson

37:24.110 --> 37:25.760
and don't do it again.

37:28.150 --> 37:29.360
Go wash your face.

37:34.410 --> 37:36.670
As service staff on the executive floor,

37:36.760 --> 37:37.590
our behavior

37:37.590 --> 37:40.190
represents the service level
of Purong Hotel.

37:40.440 --> 37:43.360
In this incident, Jia violated

37:43.360 --> 37:45.710
Puyong Hotel's HSKP Department,

37:45.810 --> 37:47.070
Article 27,

37:47.070 --> 37:48.710
by privately inspecting

37:48.710 --> 37:50.110
a guest's personal belongings.

37:50.110 --> 37:52.800
After a joint decision by
the HSKP Department and HR Department,

37:52.800 --> 37:54.190
your monthly bonus will be deducted.

37:54.190 --> 37:55.250
Do you accept this?

37:56.290 --> 37:57.210
I accept.

38:00.310 --> 38:01.840
I hope this incident

38:01.840 --> 38:03.320
will serve as a warning to everyone.

38:03.320 --> 38:04.280
Don't think that

38:04.760 --> 38:05.550
being late,

38:06.680 --> 38:08.080
gossiping about guests,

38:08.960 --> 38:10.810
slacking off, faking an illness,

38:10.810 --> 38:12.730
slipping away, or skipping work

38:12.840 --> 38:14.890
won't cause problems
just because no one sees you.

38:14.890 --> 38:16.610
I'm not doing this
to make things difficult for anyone,

38:16.610 --> 38:19.060
but to help everyone avoid risks together.

38:19.630 --> 38:21.110
Workplace competition is certainly fierce,

38:21.110 --> 38:22.170
but it's more about

38:22.320 --> 38:24.060
cooperation and mutual benefit.

38:24.060 --> 38:26.390
I may not be your friend,

38:26.420 --> 38:27.460
but

38:27.960 --> 38:29.800
I am at least your partner.

38:33.990 --> 38:34.920
As the forewoman,

38:34.920 --> 38:37.190
I hope whenever you have any difficulties,

38:37.190 --> 38:38.110
you can come to me.

38:38.110 --> 38:39.280
I will spare no effort

38:39.280 --> 38:42.010
to help everyone
accomplish our tasks together.

38:42.360 --> 38:43.560
There is only one goal.

38:43.560 --> 38:45.800
I hope everyone can do their part

38:46.190 --> 38:49.320
to improve the service
on the executive floor together.

38:49.400 --> 38:50.190
All right?

38:50.190 --> 38:51.110
Yes.

39:00.430 --> 39:01.990
[Wishing you prosperity and good fortune]

39:03.630 --> 39:05.770
Miyu sent a really big red packet.

39:06.190 --> 39:07.670
What does this mean?

39:07.890 --> 39:09.290
Penalties must be given,

39:09.370 --> 39:11.080
but compensations must also be made.

39:11.080 --> 39:12.990
This is everyone's overtime pay
from last time.

39:12.990 --> 39:15.910
Although it's still less
than what you deserve.

39:15.960 --> 39:18.420
I thought the overtime pay
wasn't approved.

39:18.480 --> 39:20.540
Are you paying out of your own pocket?

39:21.210 --> 39:22.190
My bonus from last time

39:22.190 --> 39:23.440
is completely gone.

39:23.700 --> 39:25.560
If you guys go against me again,

39:25.800 --> 39:27.280
I'll have nothing to eat.

39:31.710 --> 39:34.070
Rooms 1805 and 1807 are checking out.

39:35.900 --> 39:36.810
Copy that.

39:37.820 --> 39:38.610
Alright.

39:38.970 --> 39:39.970
Let's get to work.

39:51.940 --> 39:52.820
Xu Miyu,

39:53.040 --> 39:54.060
you can do this.

39:54.410 --> 39:55.880
You can be a good forewoman,

39:55.880 --> 39:57.230
and do this job well.

39:57.470 --> 39:58.830
You can rely on yourself,

39:58.830 --> 40:00.830
and live every day of your life well.

40:07.780 --> 40:10.340
[Purong Hotel]

40:13.630 --> 40:14.400
Mr. Qian.

40:15.150 --> 40:15.550
Mr. Ji.

40:15.550 --> 40:16.210
Have a seat.

40:18.350 --> 40:19.010
Have a seat.

40:20.400 --> 40:24.200
This is the reservation cancellation
form for Shijing Technology.

40:24.950 --> 40:26.080
Why was it canceled?

40:26.760 --> 40:28.670
They were already quite hesitant.

40:28.670 --> 40:29.280
Now,

40:29.280 --> 40:31.550
with this whole bleach incident,

40:31.010 --> 40:31.810
[Cancellation of Reservation Agreement]

40:31.550 --> 40:33.190
they are even more afraid to
give such a big order

40:32.020 --> 40:33.330
[Party A (Seal):
Shijing Technology Co., Ltd.]

40:33.190 --> 40:34.190
to us.

40:33.470 --> 40:33.850
[Cancellation of Reservation Agreement]

40:34.190 --> 40:36.400
Zhanpeng Industry is an old client,

40:36.400 --> 40:38.630
but they haven't renewed the contract.

40:39.110 --> 40:40.710
This is the written notice

40:40.710 --> 40:42.280
we sent them a month in advance.

40:42.280 --> 40:43.070
Take a look.

40:45.480 --> 40:46.540
How did they reply?

40:47.960 --> 40:49.880
They just said they're still considering,

40:49.880 --> 40:50.880
with no definite answer.

40:50.880 --> 40:53.400
We also sent people over to visit,

40:53.590 --> 40:55.720
but they either said the boss wasn't in

40:55.880 --> 40:57.710
or gave vague answers.

40:57.960 --> 40:59.000
I figured,

40:59.000 --> 41:01.280
since our agreement has expired,

41:01.590 --> 41:02.880
this weekend I'll have

41:02.880 --> 41:05.880
the front desk, housekeeping,
and finance settle the accounts

41:05.880 --> 41:06.760
and take the rooms back.
